file.name: onlyAbsoluteServersWithBasePaths.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Example OpenApi 3 spec
  description: Has an absolute server with a base path
  version: 0.1.0
servers:
  - url: http://api.example.com/basePath1
    description: absolute server with a base path
paths:
  /endpointPath:
    get:
      responses:
        200:
          description: Response body should be a string
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
